		<title>09Employment</title>
		<content>     The local colleries Taf Merthyr   
 and Deep Navigation employ many local 
 people.Others work in industries such 
 as Hoovers Pentrebach,Merthyr.In the  
 near future the Trelewis Drift mine,  
 which was open in 1950 to work the    
 coal formerly worked by the Bedlinog  
 Colliery is to close.                 
     Unemployment varies between 6% and
 10% of the working population,mainly  
 young people between 16 and 21 are    
 affected at present.                  
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
